column5: Hey all, just thought I'd let you in on a few of the prizes that will be available for Saturday, and the auction....  Just the beginning for the prize list, you'll have to come out to see the rest  fishtrap - value $265 and thats the sale price Mr buddy heater - value $100 Two coffee makers - value $150 each Plano tackle box - value ? but would guess at $80 or more  For the auction we'll have a  Guided Trip for 5-6 with Fishmaster A weekend at Lakair 1 Day guided trip on the ice 2 Days at a beautiful location in Temagami, just bring yourself and your clothes  (more to come on that, it's a big one  ) Fish Trap I-pod Nano  Again there are a few more items but I don't want to give them all away  you'll have to check it out Sat. night or Sun. Morning  Gonna be a GOOD DAY!!!!  Maureen
Gee... I wonder if I can get in on that one ? I always have to haul the boat up there... food.. tackle.. cottage maintenance. Would be so much easier to just be a drop in pest somewhere !
Even simpler than that, Wayne.  We can just crash at your place.  Lookin' forward,....  douG
